95 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;木桌上 Bose QuietComfort Earbuds II 的俯视图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0rObLjbJirFmV54H0fiWcO6qRFk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73449423/DSCF9291_3.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;QuietComfort 耳塞 II 不再是 Bose 最好的耳机，但它们仍然是花钱能买到的最好的耳塞之一。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;EU02y5&quot;>;我对“猜猜流行音乐”这个周末感到头晕目眩。这次是源源不断的烟花吗？或者持枪的德克萨斯人庆祝性地消耗弹药，无视禁止此类行为的规则？值得庆幸的是，猜谜游戏并没有持续太久——我决定放弃我选择的降噪耳塞&lt;/a>; 一次非常认真的锻炼。如果您需要一副出色的耳机来应对公共或私人骚乱，您应该查看 &lt;strong>;Bose QuietComfort 耳塞 II&lt;/strong>;，该耳机在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon 上有售.com/dp/B0B4PSQHD5?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp ;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1723138-REG%2Fbose_870730_0010_quietcomfort_earbuds_ii_noise_canceling.html&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com %2F2024%2F7%2F8%2F24194085%2Fbose-quietcomfort-earbuds-ii-tile-mate-deal-sale&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;B&amp;H 照片&lt;/a>;，黑色创纪录低价 169.95 美元（优惠 110 美元）。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;sOSySV&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore &quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Bose SoundLink Max 评论：尺寸大小的声音并不便宜&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge. com/24157693/bose-soundlink-max-speaker-review&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Bose 的 Ultra Open 耳塞是迄今为止最大胆、最独特的耳塞&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /24073019/bose-ultra-open-earbuds-review&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;摩托罗拉新款 130 美元耳塞是 Bose 合作产品 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/ 16/24132273/motorola-moto-buds-plus-bose-anc&quot;}